Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:54.88,*Default,NTP,0050,0000,0000,,{\3c&H00B000A6&\fnMicrosoft Yahei\bord5\an4\fs46}被\N發\N現\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.88,0:24:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0050,0000,,{\3c&H00B000A6&\fnMicrosoft Yahei\bord5\an6\fs46}夜\N間\N活\N動\N被\N禁\N止
